<p>Dave&#39;s back from vacation and he and John have a show packed with info, tips, and tricks just for you. Answering your questions about ethernet, time machine, mail drafts, and software updates they make sure you understand the &#8220;why&#8221; behind the &#8220;how to.&#8221; This week&#39;s episode also includes listener solutions for the folder syncing geek challenge and a few things to add to the Cool Stuff Found category. Don&#39;t miss it!</p>
